caption: #contest.    #contest it's my dream to formally meet both of you amazingly talented boys. I've been team jack and Jack for as long as I can remember. To me all your songs are hits. They are all amazing. I love both of you with all my heart. And i don't know how much more to express that. I was able to see you guys preform at the show of the summer and it was the best day of my life. It would mean everything if I could meet you again but like I said formally.  Actually talk to you and get to know each other. I miss you both sooooo much. Pleas at least read this. Love you with all my heart??????????✌?️???
